item.title: CVE-2023-4776|2023-10-16T19:38:59.813Z -- unknown -- school%20management%20system
item.description: The School Management System WordPress plugin before 2.2.5 uses the WordPress esc_sql() function on a field not delimited by quotes and did not first prepare the query, leading to a SQL injection exploitable by relatively low-privilege users like Teachers.
